>> title: Lentil Bolognese Pasta
>> cuisine: Italian
>> tags: pasta, vegan, soy-free
>> servings: 2

-- Assembly time: 12 minutes

Cook @spaghetti or linguine{8%oz} according to package in #large pot{}.

Heat @../components/proteins/lentil-bolognese{1.5%cups}.

Drain pasta, toss with bolognese sauce.

Top with @fresh basil{2%tbsp}(chopped) and @vegan parmesan{2%tbsp}.

-- Hearty, satisfying pasta with meaty lentil sauce
